    <!-- Leader Dialog -->
    <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_FIRST_MEET_LEADER_NEPHI_ANY" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Greetings! I am Nephi, son of Lehi. Behold, my people have travelled far and suffered much. It is good to meet you.</Text>
    </Row>

    <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_FIRST_MEET_VISIT_RECIPIENT_LEADER_NEPHI_ANY" Language="en_US">
      <Text>The Lord has blessed us exceedingly and we have established many cities in this promised land. Would you care to share 
	  in our blessings?</Text>
    </Row>

    <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_FIRST_MEET_NEAR_INITIATOR_POSITIVE_LEADER_NEPHI_ANY" Language="en_US">
      <Text>The Lord has blessed us exceedingly and we have established many cities in this promised land. Please, come to our temple 
	  and learn more of the blessings the Lord has in store.</Text>
